OL,3,C'This is not a two-horse race' insists
OL,4,CDeputy First Minister after ITV poll
OL,6,FLabour's Deputy First Minister has
OL,7,Finsisted tomorrow's Senedd election is
OL,8,Fnot a 'two-horse' race between Plaid
OL,9,FCymru and Reform UK.
OL,11,FSpeaking on Sharp End, Huw Irranca-
OL,12,FDavis said "the polling that we've had
OL,13,Ftonight would be disappointing for
OL,14,FLabour, you can't take away from it.
OL,16,F"But what it also shows is there are
OL,17,Freally narrow margins, particularly
OL,18,Ffor that fifth and sixth seat, and
OL,19,Fthat is where a lot of parties can
OL,20,Fmake a difference, so it's not a two-
OL,21,Fhorse race."
OL,26,@tD@LOUxD@AOU}D@LO]
