OL,3,C'This is not a two-horse race' insists
OL,4,CDeputy First Minister after ITV poll
OL,6,FPlaid Cymru has jumped ahead to be the
OL,7,Fpredicted largest party in the Senedd
OL,8,FElection, according to the latest ITV
OL,9,FCymru Wales opinion poll.
OL,11,FThe findings, released two days before
OL,12,Fpolls open, show Rhun ap Iorwerth's
OL,13,Fparty with 33% of the vote share, four
OL,14,Fpercentage points ahead of Reform UK
OL,15,Fat 29%.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
