OL,3,C'This is not a two-horse race' insists
OL,4,CDeputy First Minister after ITV poll
OL,6,FHeledd Fychan, from Plaid Cymru,
OL,7,Fargued that Thursday's election is in
OL,8,Ffact a decision between her party and
OL,9,FReform. She said, "It is very much a
OL,10,Ftwo-horse race between Reform and
OL,11,FPlaid Cymru for many of those six
OL,12,Fseats, and there's a huge risk that
OL,13,FReform could become the big us party
OL,14,Fin Wales.
OL,16,F"So we are asking people to think
OL,17,Fcarefully before they vote, because we
OL,18,Fknow the majority of people in Wales
OL,19,Fare terrified by the prospect of a
OL,20,Freformed government."
OL,26,@qD@SOUxD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
