OL,3,C'This is not a two-horse race' insists
OL,4,CDeputy First Minister after ITV poll
OL,6,FThe Conservatives' Tom Giffard said,
OL,7,F"If you vote Conservative and you are
OL,8,Fa Conservative, you'll get
OL,9,FConservative representation; no
OL,10,Fparty's going to win a majority.
OL,12,F"So having strong conservative voices
OL,13,Fin that next unit will really matter.
OL,14,FSo if you are a Conservative out
OL,15,Fthere, don't overthink it, don't vote
OL,16,Ftactically, vote Conservative, and
OL,17,Fyou'll get Conservative."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@YO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/9
