OL,3,C'This is not a two-horse race' insists
OL,4,CDeputy First Minister after ITV poll
OL,6,FThe Green Party has dropped into fifth
OL,7,Fplace at 8%, which in yesterday's
OL,8,Fround of results would only net them
OL,9,Ftwo seats in Caerdydd Ffynnon Taf and
OL,10,FCaerdydd Penarth.
OL,12,FPhilip Davies, from the Greens, said,
OL,13,F"Small wins in voting percentages for
OL,14,Fthe Green Party in specific seats will
OL,15,Fmean we win those sixth seats instead
OL,16,Fof Reform.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
