SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1778087158
OL,3,C'This is not a two-horse race' insists
OL,4,CDeputy First Minister after ITV poll
OL,6,F"So what we're really going to do is
OL,7,Fgo out there and vote for who they
OL,8,Fwant to be in the Senedd, because
OL,9,Fthat's what people want. People want
OL,10,Factual change; we haven't been in the
OL,11,FSenedd before. We're not going in as
OL,12,Fcareer politicians; we're going as
OL,13,Fpeople who actually want to make big
OL,14,Fpositive change for our nation."
OL,16,FThe Welsh Lib Dems have held at 6%,
OL,17,Fwhich could elect leader Jane Dodds in
OL,18,FBrycheiniog Tawe Nedd.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@`O]
