OL,3,C'This is not a two-horse race' insists
OL,4,CDeputy First Minister after ITV poll
OL,6,FTim Sly from the Welsh Liberal
OL,7,FDemocrats said, "I think what the poll
OL,8,Fdoesn't reflect is the fact that we
OL,9,Ffought a campaign which is hyper-
OL,10,Ffocused on a small number of target
OL,11,Fseats, and our expectation is that we
OL,12,Fwill make gains and we will be well up
OL,13,Fon the one seat that's predicted.
OL,15,F"I'd also point out that in the 2024
OL,16,Fgeneral election, most of the polls
OL,17,Fhad the Lib Dems nationally on 20 to
OL,18,F30 seats, who ended up winning 72, so
OL,19,Fthat's all to play for.
OL,26,@oD@QOUwD@AOU
